---
title: 'Strong Password Generator'
description: 'Generate strong passwords with alphabets, numbers and special characters or generate password with phrases.'
layout: 'tools'
styles:
  - 'styles/passwordgen.css'
scripts:
  - 'https://unpkg.com/vue@2.0.3/dist/vue.js'
  - 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/clipboard.js/1.6.0/clipboard.min.js'
  - 'scripts/passhelp.min.js'
  - 'scripts/passwordgen.js'
---

#app
  .section.container-readable
    h2.h4 Generated Password
    input#password(type="text", v-model="password")
    .text-small.text-muted.text-center
      button.button-ghost.button-copy(data-clipboard-target="#password") Copy Password
      button.button(@click='count++') Generate Another
    
    label.mt2 Password Type
    <input type="radio" id="strong" value="strong" v-model="type">
    <label class="label-inline" for="strong">Strong Password (Alphanumeric with special characters)</label>
    <br>
    <input type="radio" id="alphanumeric" value="alphanumeric" v-model="type">
    <label class="label-inline" for="alphanumeric">Alphanumeric Password</label>
    <br>
    <input type="radio" id="phrase" value="phrase" v-model="type">
    <label class="label-inline" for="phrase">Phrase Password</label>
    <br>
    <input type="radio" id="phrase_special_chars" value="phrase_special_chars" v-model="type">
    <label class="label-inline" for="phrase_special_chars">Phrase Password with special characters</label>

    label.mt2 Password Length (<span v-html="unit"></span>)
    input(type="number", v-model="length", style="width: 50%;")

.container-readable
  .section
    h2.h3 How to Generate Strong Password?
    ul.divider
      li A strong password will be automatically generated on page load which you can copy using the 'Copy Password' button.
      li Default option is to generate a strong password with alphabets, numbers and special characters of length 15.
      li You can change the password type to just alphanumeric, phrases or phrases with special charcaters.
      li You can also specify the character length or word length (in case of phrases) for generating password.
      li You may want to use a password manager to remember the generated password as you will not be able to retrieve it back from this site.
      li We do not store any of the generated passwords and everything is done inside your browser.
